quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alɩf, Laam, Raa, woto yaa Gafã Aayar-rãmb la Alkʋrãan sẽn vẽnegde."
  15,2,"Kɩfr-rãmbã na n wa tʋll n nongɑme n yɩẽ moeembɑ [sak-n-tũ-rãmba]."
  15,3,"Bas-b tɩ b rɩtẽ la b maan wʋm-noogo, tɩ tẽebã liibd-ba, ad b na wɑ n bãnge."
  15,4,"Lɑ Tõnd pa halkd tẽngɑ, rẽndame t'a rɑ tara wɑkɑt b sẽn mi."
  15,5,"Zãma pɑ tõe n reng a wakato, a leb n pa tõe n yaoolg-a ye."
  15,6,"Tɩ b (Mak-rãmbã) yeele: ""yaa foom b sẽn sik Alkʋrãanã n kõ-ɑ soabã, ad fo sɩd yaa gãeenga."
  15,7,"Bõe yĩng tɩ fo pa nɑ n wa ne malεgs tõng nengẽ, sã n mikame tɩ f yaa sɩd soaba?"""
  15,8,"Tõnd pa sikd malεgsã rẽndame tɩ yɩ ne sɩda, la wakat-kãngã, b pa na n koll-b ye."
  15,9,"Ad yaa Tõnd n sik Alkʋrãanã, la ad yaa Tõnd n gũud-a."
  15,10,"La ad Tõnd tʋma sẽn reng fo taoore tɩ kẽng rẽenem rãmbã sulẽ wã."
  15,11,"Tẽn-tʋʋm buud pa wat bãmbã nengẽ, rẽndame tɩ b yɩ n yaand-a."
  15,12,"Yaa woto bɑl la Tõnd kẽesd-ɑ (kɩɩsgã) nin-wẽnsã sũy."
  15,13,"B pɑ kõt sɩd ne-ɑ lae (Alkʋrãanã) lɑ ɑd pĩnd rãmbã lembɑ b pʋɩɩre tɩ looge."
  15,14,"Lɑ baa tɩ Tõnd sã n pak ragnoor sɑɑgẽ wã, tɩ b kel n rʋʋd be"
  15,15,"B ra na n yeelame: ""ad b rɑɑgɑ tõnd ninã, b pʋs n maana tõnd tɩɩm."
  15,16,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd ninga saagẽ wã ãdse, la D le nags-a ne ɑ gεtbã."
  15,17,"La D leb n gũ-a n yi sʋtãan fãa b sẽn rig n zãɑg Wẽnd yolsgã."
  15,18,"Sã n pa sẽn zukɑ n kelge, tɩ bug-vɩleng sẽn yaa vẽeneg pʋglg-ɑ."
  15,19,"La tẽn-gãngã, Tõnd yεdg-a lame la D ning a zug tãn-bεd la D buls a pʋgẽ bũmbã fãa tɩ zemse."
  15,20,"La D ning a pʋgẽ rɩbd yãmb yĩngɑ la D rɩlgd bõn-vɩɩls ɑ tɑɑb yãmb sẽn pa rɩlgde."
  15,21,"Lɑ bũmb buud pɑ be rẽndɑme tɩ Tõnd tar a kʋlem-biisã la Tõnd pa sikd-ɑ rẽnda sẽn nɑ zems bɑlɑ."
  15,22,"La Tõnd tʋma sebgã t'a leegd sɑwɑtã tɩ D sik saasẽ wã koom n yũnug yãmb ne-ɑ la yãmb rɑg n pa tõe n kogl-ɑ ye."
  15,23,"Lɑ ɑd yaa Tõnd n vɩɩmsd la D kʋʋda, la leb n yaa Tõnd la faad rɩkdba."
  15,24,"Ad Tõnd mii yãmb sʋkã neb nins sẽn deng taoore, la Tõnd le mi neb nins sẽn yaoolbã."
  15,25,"Ad fo Soabã n na n tigim-b gilli, ad A yaa bʋʋd mita n yaa mitɑ."
  15,26,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd naana ninsaal ne yagd sɑblg sẽn yɑɑ koεɛng koe-koe."
  15,27,"La sã n yaa zĩn-rãmbã, Tõnd reng n naan-b lame ne bug-zirga."
  15,28,"Tẽeg fo Soabã sẽn wa n yeel malεgsã: "" Ad Mam na n naana ninsaal ne yagd-sɑblg sẽn yɑɑ koɛɛng koe-koe."
  15,29,"La M sã n wa sɑɑs-a n fʋʋs M vɩɩmã ɑ pʋgẽ, bɩ y lʋɩ n maan-a suguudu."
  15,30,"Tɩ malεgsã fãa gill maan-a suguudu."
  15,31,"Sã n pa a ɭblɩɩs sẽn zãgs t'ɑ pa nɑ n lɑgem suguud maandbã."
  15,32,"Tɩ Wẽnd yeele:"" ɭblɩɩsa, bõe n tar foom tɩ f pa lɑgem suguud maandbẽ? """
  15,33,"T'a yeele: ""mam pa yɩ n na n maan ninsaal suguud ye; Fo naan-a-la ne yagd-sɑblg sẽn yɑɑ koɛɛng koe-koe."
  15,34,"T'A yeele: "" bɩ f yi [arzãnã pʋga] bala fo yaa b sẽn rig n zãag yolsgo!"
  15,35,"La kãab beed be ne foom n tɩ tãag dĩinã yaoob raare!"""
  15,36,"T'a yeele: m Soaba, bɩ F koll maam n tɩ tãag raar ning B sẽn na n yik-ba"""
  15,37,"T'A yeele: "" rẽnd fo naaga b sẽn na n koll-b rãmbã."
  15,38,"Hal n tɩ ta raar wɑkɑt sẽn mi."
  15,39,"T'a yeele:"" m Soaba, Fo sẽn menes maamã yĩnga, mam na n faasa wẽngã b yĩng tẽn-gãngã zugu, lɑ m na n menemsa b fãa gilli."
  15,40,"Sã n pa Fo yembsã sẽn yaa F sẽn yɩlg-b rãmbã""."
  15,41,"T'A yeele: ""ad wãnde yaa so-tɩrg sẽn tɑɑsd Mam nengẽ."
  15,42,"Ad Mam yembsã, fo pa tar pãng b zug ye, rẽnda ned ning sẽn tũ foom n naag neb sẽn kedge."
  15,43,"Lɑ ɑd gεhannem la b fãa sεk zĩiga."
  15,44,"A tara noy a yopoe, noor fãa bãmb pεdg tara b pʋɩɩr be."
  15,45,"Ad wẽn-zoεtbã bee arzãn-rãmb la ko-nin pʋgẽ."
  15,46,"Kẽ-y-yã-a ne laafɩ, n yaa bas-m-yam rãmba."
  15,47,"Tɩ Tõnd yiis sũ-kĩir fãa b sũyẽ wã, tɩ b lebg ma-biisi, n be gãas zut n tees taaba."
  15,48,"Yaams pa paamd-b ɑ pʋgẽ, b leb n pa na n yiis-b be ye."
  15,49,"Kõ M yembsã kɩbar tɩ yaa Maam la yaafg naab n yaa yolsg naaba."
  15,50,"La Mam sɩbgrã me n yaa sɩbg toaaga."
  15,51,"Leb n kõ-b kɩbar sẽn kẽed ne a ɭbraahɩɩm sãambã."
  15,52,"B sẽn wa n kẽ a nengẽ n yeele: ""Salaam"" tɩlgr bɑlɑ, t'a yeele: "" ad tõnd yaεεsda yãmba""."
  15,53,"Tɩ b yeele: ""ra yaεεs ye! Tõnd kõta foom koe-noog ne biig sẽn yɑɑ bãngdɑ."
  15,54,"T'a yeele: yãmb kõta maam koe-no-kãngã tɩ mam yaool n lebga kãsema? Yaa bõe sũ-noogre?"
  15,55,"Tɩ b yeele: ad tõnd noogɑ fo sũur ne sɩda, bɩ f ra yɩ tẽeb wãagd ye."
  15,56,"T'a yeele: "" lɑ ãnd n wãagd a tẽeb ne Wẽnd yolsgã, sã n pa menemdbã?"""
  15,57,"La a yeele: "" bõe la yãmb rata yãmb ɑ tẽn-tʋmdbã?"""
  15,58,"Tɩ b yeele: "" ad b tʋma tõnd tɩ d kẽng nin-wẽnsẽ wã,"
  15,59,"Rẽnda a Lʋʋt zakã rãmbɑ, tõnd na n põsga b gilli,"
  15,60,"Rẽnda a pagã bala, ""Tõnd bʋʋme t'a na n zĩndɑ halkdbã pʋga."
  15,61,"La tẽn-tʋʋmdbã sẽn wa n wa a Lʋʋt zakã rãmbẽ wã."
  15,62,"A yeelɑme: ""ad yãmb yaa nin-sãambse""."
  15,63,"Tɩ b yeele: ""ayo, tõnd waa fo nengẽ ne bũmb ning bãmb sẽn da yɩ n maan sikã''."
  15,64,"D waa fo nengẽ ne sɩdã, la tõnd yaa sɩd-rãmba."
  15,65,"Bɩ f yi yʋng ne f zakã rãmba, la f pʋg b poorã, la yãmb ned ba a ye ra wẽneg a poorẽ ye, lɑ tees-y b sẽn saglẽ yãmbã."
  15,66,"La Tõnd togs a Lʋʋt yel-kãngɑ: tɩ ad bãmbã yẽgrã na n wãɑgɑ be-vẽer wɑkato."
  15,67,"Tɩ (Sɑdʋʋm) tẽngã rãmb wa n kɩdemdẽ."
  15,68,"T'a yeele: ""ad bãmbã yaa mam sãamba, ra ning-y-m yãnd ye."
  15,69,"Lɑ zoe-y Wẽnd la y ra yãndg-m ye."
  15,70,"La b yeele: ""rẽ yĩnga, tõnd pa gɩdg foom tɩ f ra reeg nebã sãando?"""
  15,71,"T'a yeele: ""ad bãmbã yaa mam kom-pugli tɩ yãmb sã n rat (n furi)."
  15,72,"M wẽen ne fo vɩɩmã! Ad b be b suubã pʋgẽ n tuumdẽ."
  15,73,"Tɩ tãsgã rɩk-b winto-pukr wɑkɑto."
  15,74,"Tɩ Tõnd lebg (tẽngã) ɑ tẽngr n ning yĩngri la D kɩt tɩ kug sẽn yɑɑ tãn-wʋmi ni b zugu."
  15,75,"Ad woto yaa tagmas ne neb nins sẽn yɑɑ tɑgs-n-ges rãmbã."
  15,76,"Lɑ ɑd (tẽng-kãngã) bee so-rɑoog zugu, (tɩ b gillã fãa mi-a)."
  15,77,"Ad bee rẽndɑ pʋgẽ sẽn yaa tɑgs-n-gesg ne sɩd-kõtbã."
  15,78,"Ad Al-Ayka tẽngã rãmb me ra yɩɩ wẽgdba."
  15,79,"Tɩ Tõnd maan-b n role, la ad (tẽn-bãmbã) b yiibã bee so-rɑoog zug tɩ yɑɑ vẽenegɑ."
  15,80,"Lɑ ɑd Al-higr tẽngã rãmb rag n yagsa tẽn-tʋʋmdbã."
  15,81,"Lɑ Tõnd rag n kõ-b-la Tõnd tagmas-rãmbã tɩ b rɑ bɑlldẽ n yit-bɑ."
  15,82,"B ra bogda tãensã n maand roto, n tɑr bɑs-m-yɑm."
  15,83,"Tɩ tãsgã rɩk-b be-vẽer wɑkɑto."
  15,84,"Tɩ b sẽn da yɩ n bɑoodẽ wã pa naf-b ye."
  15,85,"La Tõnd pa naan saasã la tẽngã la bũmb ning sẽn be b yiibã sʋkã, rẽnda ne sɩda, lɑ ad Wakatã (dũni wã yikrã) sɩd nɑ n waame, sik ka be ye, bɩ f maan bɑs-tɩ-loog sẽn be neere."
  15,86,"Ad fo Soabã la Naanda, n yaa minim naaba."
  15,87,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd kõo foom Aayay a yopoe sẽn karemd n yɩlemdẽ, lɑ Alkʋrãan wagallã."
  15,88,"Ra tool f nin a yiibã n get bũmb ning Tõnd sẽn wʋms-b noog kõbg toor-toorã ye, ra leb n sãam f sũur b zug ye, la sik f meng ne sɩd-kõtbã."
  15,89,"La f yeele: ""maɑm lɑ bugsd sẽn yaa vẽenega''."
  15,90,"Tɩ bũmb ning Tõnd sẽn sik welgdbã zugã buud rɑ wɑ pɑɑm-y ye,"
  15,91,"Neb nins sẽn mɑɑn Alkʋrãanã peds-pedsã."
  15,92,"Ne fo Soabã yõore, D na n sogsa b fãa gilli"
  15,93,"B sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  15,94,"Bɩ f vẽneg b sẽn sagl foom ne bũmb ningã la f bɑll n yi lagem-n-taɑrã rãmbɑ."
  15,95,"Tõnd na n gũu foom n yi yĩgsdbã."
  15,96,"Sẽn lagem-b soob-dãmb a taab ne Wẽndã, b na wɑ n bãnge."
  15,97,"Lɑ ɑd Tõnd miime tɩ fo sãamda f sũur ne b sẽn yetã."
  15,98,"Bɩ f yɩlg f Soabã ne pẽgre la f yɩ n naag pʋʋsdbã."
  15,99,"La tũ f Soabã hal tɩ sɩdã (kũumã) wa wa foom."
